{{PBB|geneid=3576}}
'''白细胞介素-8'''（{{lang-en|Interleukin-8}}，简称为'''白介素-8'''或'''IL-8'''，亦称为趋化因子'''CXCL8'''）是[[巨噬细胞|巨噬细胞]]和[[上皮细胞|上皮细胞]]等分泌的[[细胞因子|细胞因子]]<ref name=bag>Baggiolini, M.; Walz, A.; Kunkel, S. L. Neutrophil-activating peptide-1/interleukin 8, a novel cytokine that activates neutrophils. J. Clin. Invest. 84: 1045-1049, 1989.</ref>。白细胞介素-8结合趨化因子受体白细胞介素-8受体α(IL8RA, 又叫[[CXCR1|CXCR1]])和白细胞介素-8受体β(IL8RB, 又叫[[CXCR2|CXCR2]])而对嗜中性粒细胞(neutrophils)有细胞趋化作用而实现其对炎症反应的调节<ref name=ahu>Ahuja SK, Ozcelik T, Milatovitch A, Francke U, Murphy PM. Molecular evolution of the human interleukin-8 receptor gene cluster. Nat Genet. 1992 Sep;2(1):31-6.</ref><ref name=bag>Baggiolini, M.; Walz, A.; Kunkel, S. L. Neutrophil-activating peptide-1/interleukin 8, a novel cytokine that activates neutrophils. J. Clin. Invest. 84: 1045-1049, 1989.</ref>。 白细胞介素-8还有很强的促血管生成作用。白细胞介素-8在[[小支气管炎|小支气管炎]]<ref>Emi, M. et al., Association of diffuse panbronchiolitis with microsatellite polymorphism of the human interleukin 8 (IL-8) gene. J. Hum. Genet. 44: 169-172, 1999.</ref> 和[[囊性纤维化|囊性纤维化]]<ref>Srivastava, M. et al., Digitoxin mimics gene therapy with CFTR and suppresses hypersecretion of IL-8 from cystic fibrosis lung epithelial cells. Proc. Nat. Acad. Sci. 101: 7693-7698, 2004.</ref> 的发病中起重要作用。

